tool_description: Solves different types of captcha using pageurl and sitekey.
name: Fast MultiSolver
title: Fast MultiSolver

api_list.name: Get Response
api_list.description:
Get response based on the input ID received from create request.
Send a request every 5 seconds to get the response. Anything apart from CAPCHA_NOT_READY and OK|token is an invalid response and you should stop making request for the ID.

required_parameters.name: id
required_parameters.description: Enter the id received from Create Request API. Do not use OK| in id while sending the request.
